race.comment: BIT TIRED ACTUALLY (10) just missed fresh but showed she was up to this level last start when flying home over this track and trip. Nottle claiming 3kgs will see her with no weight on her back and the filly is trending the right way. Strikes a winnable race here. LORD MOMO (5)  is on debut for the Vahala stable following a 0.4L defeat in a recent trial at Belmont. He moved well there over 1200m and his trip fresh looks ideal. Looks to have some class about him and can play a leading role on debut. MAGIC CARATS (3) flew home first-up and looks beautifully placed out in trip now. Can put his best foot forward. SAVIENNE (12) can turn in a bold debut out to 1400m on debut.
